    <title>mac安装Matlab2014a</title>
    <link href="http://wongchen.github.io/2016/11/11/mac%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Matlab2014a/"/>
    <id>http://wongchen.github.io/2016/11/11/mac安装Matlab2014a/</id>
    <published>2016-11-11T12:26:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-11-11T12:57:15.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装Matlab 2014a后，打开时，遇到一些Java错误信息，解决方法：<br>到<strong>官网</strong>下载<a href="https://www.mathworks.com/support/bugreports/1098655" target="_blank" rel="external">R2014a_patch_1098655</a>补丁，一定要去官网下载，找到对应的版本号，运行下载的程序，选择要patch的程序Matlab，OK。</p>
<p>对于带有Retina Display的mac，打开进去后会发现分辨率很低，这是由于安装的matlab内建的jre所导致。解决方法：<br><br></p>
<ol>
<li>安装JDK，去<a href="http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html" target="_blank" rel="external">官网</a>哦，若已安装，忽略。<br></li>
<li>修改Matlab的JAVA环境变量,终端执行<br><code>echo &quot;MATLAB_JAVA=/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdkXX_XX.jdk/Contents/Home/jre&quot; &gt;&gt; ~/.bash_profile</code></li>
<li>Matlab内建的jre目录为<code>/Applications/MATLAB_R2014a.app/sys/java/jre/maci64</code>，备份或删除其jre,之后创建软链接</li>
</ol>
   <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ln -s /Library/Internet\ Plug-Ins/JavaAppletPlugin.plugin/Contents/Home/ jre</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>   没啥多说的，只是网上找的好些都有错误。</p>
]]></content>
    
